#

Tofu and Vegetable Stir-Fry

25 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-free

Cuisine:

Asian

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

QuickHealthyVegetarian

Description

A vibrant and colorful stir-fry packed with nutritious vegetables and protein-rich tofu, all tossed in a savory sauce.

Ingredients

  • firm tofu: 1 block
  • bell peppers: 1 cup, sliced
  • broccoli florets: 1 cup
  • carrots: 1 medium, sliced thinly
  • soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • ginger: 1 teaspoon, minced
  • sesame seeds: 1 tablespoon (optional)
  • green onions: 2, chopped (for garnish)
